<item>
            <title>[LU-8095] switch LNET_* static function names to lower case</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8095</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Replace the upper-case names with lower-case names for the following static inline functions from LNet:&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_NIDADDR&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_NIDNET&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_MKNID&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_NETNUM&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_NETTYP&lt;br/&gt;
    LNET_MKNET&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="36563">LU-8095</key>
            <summary>switch LNET_* static function names to lower case</summary>
